Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.74,0:01:48.78,Naslov S,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\fs50\fax-0.27\fay-0.098\bord2\blur2\frz4.845\c&H8E4722&\pos(976,591)}www.anime-overdose.com\Nprevod i obrada: Knez Miloš
