Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.34,0:23:37.92,Default,Hibi,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Još dvadeset minuta kiseonika.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.92,0:23:39.73,Default,Dami,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}N-Ne vredi...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.73,0:23:40.78,Default,Dami,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tako je hladno.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.78,0:23:41.64,Default,Bud,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Dovraga...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.94,0:23:46.02,Default,Bud,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Bubi će trebati više od dvadeset minuta do Hibita!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.30,0:23:48.19,Default,Bud,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Nećemo stići na vreme!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.19,0:23:51.97,Default,Hibi,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ako ću već da umrem, bolje da opet padnem u onu uvalu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.97,0:23:54.82,Default,Hibi,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}kako bih video zvezdano nebo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.82,0:23:56.08,Default,Hibi,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Najbolje tako.
