Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.40,0:24:00.00,Default,Mu,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hibito...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.64,0:24:02.53,Default,Mu,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}ja se ne brinem,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.53,0:24:03.59,Default,Mu,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}pa se neću moliti.
